>void mca_set_dma_mode </CODE
>(unsigned int dmanr, unsigned int mode);</CODE
></P
><P
></P
></DIV
></DIV
><DIV
CLASS="refsect1"
><A
NAME="AEN672"
></A
><H2
>Argumentos</H2
